Package: com.sinfool.nofadetoblackunlockanimations
Name: No 'Fade To Black' Unlock Animations  ₉₋₅₋₁₅ ⚑
Author: Sinfool
Description: Disables the 'fade to black' transition animation (from LS to HS/Apps) when unlocking.  This 'crossfade' occurs when/if...  Disables the 'fade to black' transition animation (from LS to HS/Apps) when unlocking.  This 'crossfade' occurs when/if... 
 .
 - (1) Different wallpapers are set for the LS & HS
 - (2) An app is in the foreground
 .
 Made after reading a request via r/jailbreak.
 .
 FYI:  You may want to use this along with the patch titled "No Unlock Animations (disables icon zooming)".
 .
 [v.2] Tested with an iP6+ 8.4.  (9-5-15)
 .
 ⚑ UPDATES:
